#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matching tiles are such tiles where the face pictograms match exactly."
msgstr "マッチする牌とは、牌の絵柄が完全に一致する牌のことです。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168 index.docbook:178 index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "注:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are exceptions to this rule! In the traditional game of Mahjong "
#| "each tile has a matching one except for the <quote>Flowers</quote> and "
#| "<quote>Seasons</quote> tiles."
msgid ""
"There are exceptions to this rule. In the traditional game of Mahjong each "
"tile has a matching one except for the <quote>Flowers</quote> and "
"<quote>Seasons</quote> tiles."
msgstr ""
"このルールには例外があります。伝統的なマージャンでは、花牌と季節牌以外の牌は "
"1 セットに 2 つずつあります。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <quote>Flowers</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
#| "matched directly to each-other."
msgid ""
"The <quote>Flowers</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
"matched directly to each other."
msgstr ""
"花牌は 1 セットに 1 つしかないので、絵柄の異なる花牌同士をマッチさせることが"
"できます。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <quote>Seasons</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
#| "matched directly to each-other."
msgid ""
"The <quote>Seasons</quote> tiles have no doubles in the set and can be "
"matched directly to each other."
msgstr ""
"季節牌は 1 セットに 1 つしかないので、絵柄の異なる季節牌同士をマッチさせるこ"
"とができます。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tiles can only be removed if they can be connected with a maximum of three "
"connected lines that do not cross any other tile. Lines can be horizontal or "
"vertical, but not diagonal."
msgstr ""
"2 つの牌は他の牌にかからない 3 本以内の水平または垂直な線で結べる場合にのみ取"
"り除くことができます。斜めの線では結べません。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You don't have to draw the lines by yourself, the game does this for you. "
#| "Just mark two matching tiles on the board, if they can be connected by a "
#| "line with no more than two bends, the line is drawn and the tiles are "
#| "removed."
msgid ""
"You do not have to draw the lines by yourself, the game does this for you. "
"Just mark two matching tiles on the board, if they can be connected by a "
"line with at most two bends, the line is drawn and the tiles are removed."
msgstr ""
"ユーザ自身が線を引く必要はありません。取り除ける 2 つの牌をクリックすると、自"
"動的に線が引かれ、ボードから取り除かれます。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Lines may only cross the empty border."
msgid "Lines may only cross empty areas of the board."
msgstr "線は他の牌がないところにのみ引けます。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Some games are unsolvable. If you would like to avoid unsolvable games "
#| "uncheck the option <guilabel>Allow unsolvable games</guilabel> in the "
#| "configuration dialog."
msgid ""
"Some games are unsolvable. If you would like to avoid unsolvable games check "
"the option <guilabel>Create solvable games only</guilabel> in the "
"configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"解けないボードもあります。そのようなボードを除外するには、設定ダイアログで "
"<guilabel>解けないゲームを許可する</guilabel> のチェックを外してください。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The scores are awarded for the quantity of the tiles removed within the "
#| "time of completion."
msgid ""
"The scores are awarded for the time the player needs to remove all the tiles "
"from the game board. Games with more tiles give more scores."
msgstr "スコアは取り除いた牌の数とそれに要した時間によって計算されます。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you played with the <guilabel>Gravity</guilabel> setting enabled, the "
"score will be doubled."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>重力</guilabel> を有効にしてプレイした場合、スコアは 2 倍になりま"
"す。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be eligible for a place amongst the high scores player has to complete a "
"game instance within the shortest period of time possible."
msgstr ""
"ハイスコアを出すには、できるだけ短い時間でゲームを完了しなければなりません。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the player uses <quote>cheat</quote> feature his/her record will not "
#| "be considered as a high score."
msgid ""
"If the player uses the <quote>Undo</quote> or <quote>Hint</quote> feature "
"the record will not be considered as a high score."
msgstr "「ヒント」を使った場合のスコアはハイスコアにはなりません。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tips"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the player uses <quote>cheat</quote> feature his/her record will not "
#| "be considered as a high score."
msgid ""
"Click on a tile with the &RMB; to highlight all matching tiles on the board. "
"Unlike using the <quote>Undo</quote> or <quote>Hint</quote> feature, this "
